snippet.title: Welcome to Urban Strife Dev Channel!
snippet.description:
Save the world, or have fun going down with it. Meet new people. Shoot new people. Old school Turn Based Strategy with post-apoc Survival and deep RPG, developed by White Pond Studio and published by MicroProse. 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/710230/Urban_Strife/
